# Detailed Procedure {#detailed-procedure .unnumbered}

##  {#section .unnumbered}

-   Log in to the Shared Folder, navigate to the designated folder.​​

-   Share the current week's folder with each GM by Wednesday so they
    can upload the relevant Aged Debtor reports and PM reports.
    (Screenshot 1, callout 1)

![](media/image4.png){width="4.896527777777778in" height="3.15in"}

-   Ensure all GMs upload the relevant Aged Debtor reports for all
    properties to the folder by Friday EOD.

-   After all reports have been uploaded, review and confirm that every
    required report is correctly visible in the folder. (Screenshot 2,
    callout 1)

![](media/image5.png){width="4.916666666666667in"
height="2.691666666666667in"}

-   Open the Aged Debt Report Summary file, copy the previous week's
    sheet, and rename it with the current week-ending date. (Screenshot
    3, callout 1)

-   In the new sheet, clear all previous week's data in columns C to H
    (amounts and comments). (Screenshot 3, callout 2)

![](media/image7.png){width="6.360416666666667in"
height="3.187007874015748in"}

-   Open the separate hotel's aged balance report, check the values in
    column H (PM/Permanent Folios 2 days+) (Screenshot 4, callout 1)

![](media/image9.png){width="6.4847222222222225in"
height="3.2193186789151356in"}

-   Copy the total of column E to column I (Screenshot 5, callout 1)

-   Paste the updated values into the Summary Aged Debtor Report under
    the relevant hotel column (Columns C to G). (Screenshot 5, callout
    2)

![](media/image11.png){width="6.560416666666667in"
height="3.3409087926509184in"}

-   Check the value in column H (PM), Cross-check the PM value with the
    PM report received from the GM.

-   After verification, update the PM value in the Summary Aged Debtor
    Report. (Screenshot 6, callout 1)

![](media/image13.png){width="5.878787182852143in"
height="3.516178915135608in"}

-   ![](media/image15.png){width="5.1818186789151355in"
    height="3.946527777777778in"}Copy all notes (if any) from each
    hotel's Aged Balance Report and paste them into the Summary Aged
    Debtor Report (Screenshot 7, callout 1)

-   Once all hotels are updated, rename the Summary Aged Debtor Report
    using the correct date. (Screenshot 8, callout 1)

![](media/image17.png){width="6.330508530183727in"
height="2.7966097987751533in"}

