##  {#section-1 .unnumbered}

**Haydock PM Report**

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Error**                          **Error Type**
  ---------------------------------- ------------------------------------
  Room No                            Fatal

  Name                               Fatal

  VIP                                Fatal

  Company                            Fatal

  Arrival                            Fatal

  Departure                          Fatal

  Room Type                          Fatal

  Prs                                Fatal

  Balance                            Fatal
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

**Aged Report - (Each Hotel)**

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Error**                          **Error Type**
  ---------------------------------- ------------------------------------
  Hotel                              Fatal

  Debtor Days: \<30                  Fatal

  Debtor Days: 30 - 59               Fatal

  Debtor Days: 60 - 89               Fatal

  Debtor Days: 90 - 119              Fatal

  Debtor Days: 120+                  Fatal

  PM / Permanent folios 7 days       Fatal

  Total                              Fatal

  Analysis of Debt 60 Days +:        Fatal
  Balance                            

  Analysis of Debt 60 Days +:        Fatal
  Movement                           

  Rank: Lowest Debtor days           Fatal

  Bad Debt Accrual to Add            Fatal

  Totals (Each age bucket)           Fatal
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

**Aged Report - (Console Report)**

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Error**                          **Error Type**
  ---------------------------------- ------------------------------------
  Hotel                              Fatal

  Debtor Days: \<30                  Fatal

  Debtor Days: 30 - 59               Fatal

  Debtor Days: 60 - 89               Fatal

  Debtor Days: 90 - 119              Fatal

  Debtor Days: 120+                  Fatal

  PM / Permanent folios 7 days       Fatal

  Total                              Fatal

  \% Overall Debt                    Fatal

  Analysis of Debt 60 Days +:        Fatal
  Balance                            

  Analysis of Debt 60 Days +:        Fatal
  Movement since 05 Nov              

  Bad Debt Accrual to Add            Fatal

  Totals (Each age bucket)           Fatal

  Group % split by month             Fatal

  Group % split by 60-day period     Fatal

  Notes: for each Hotel              Non-Fatal
